MCNP6 test with LAQGSM03.03: 800 MeV/A C12+C12 -> pi+ invariant spectra
c E^3sigma/d^3p [mb/GeV^2/c^-3/sr] at 15, 45, 70, 90, and 145 deg
c and pi- invariant spectra at at 20, 40, 56, 90, and 145 deg (+/- 2.5 deg)
c to compare with Nagamiya's et al. measurements (LBL-8463)
c and results by LAQGSM03.03 as a stand alone code
c and to check how MCNP6 tallies separately particles and antiparticles
c using the DBCN(27) = -1 option
1   1  -10   -501      imp:h=1
2   0         501  -502  imp:h=1
99  0         502      imp:h=0

501   so 0.01
502   so 1
c
c  tally surfaces
c
125    kz    0    0.049148523     1  $ tan(12.5 deg)^2
175    kz    0    0.099413326     1  $ tan(17.5 deg)^2
225    kz    0    0.171572875     1  $ tan(22.5 deg)^2
375    kz    0    0.588790706     1  $ tan(37.5 deg)^2
425    kz    0    0.83966282      1  $ tan(42.5 deg)^2
